{"type":"message","id":"972fb42b","parentId":"f3a8b216","timestamp":"2026-03-24T16:26:48.601Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_lhar2cwbih5c_1","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5221\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3004\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] a\r\n[mutation proposed] a\r\n[master a4970b8] pulse: 2026-03-24 122615\n 6 files changed, 315 insertions(+), 83 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 122615.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 122615.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 122515.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 122615 - The CFI analysis revealed that 44.8% of invariants are pure noise (CFI=0) while only 5.7% are true causal anchors (CFI>=0.7). The natural next step is implementing the CFI-weighted compression experiment to test if CFI filtering improves next-pulse prediction versus the frequency baseline.\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"crisp-seaslug","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 5221\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3004\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] a\r\n[mutation proposed] a\r\n[master a4970b8] pulse: 2026-03-24 122615\n 6 files changed, 315 insertions(+), 83 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 122615.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 122615.mutation\n rename mutations/{proposed => rejected}/2026-03-24 122515.mutation (100%)\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 122615 - The CFI analysis revealed that 44.8% of invariants are pure noise (CFI=0) while only 5.7% are true causal anchors (CFI>=0.7). The natural next step is implementing the CFI-weighted compression experiment to test if CFI filtering improves next-pulse prediction versus the frequency baseline.\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":fal