ne being created right now. The timestamp shows when this pulse completed.","thinkingSignature":"053c8cf133c36229a052b081cb10c24c63e42419a1dbd57a63235a536f7cb019"},{"type":"text","text":"**Sandbox Pulse Summary — 2026-03-24 12:25 PM**\n\nThe previous pulse cycle (which produced the log) completed its work on the **Causal Fidelity Index (CFI) analysis** from prior sessions. It found that **44.8% of invariants are pure noise** (CFI=0) and only **5.7% are true causal anchors** (CFI≥0.7).\n\n**This pulse's mutation:** Created `research/CFI_EXPERIMENT_SPEC.md` — a detailed experiment design for comparing CFI-weighted compression vs. frequency-only baseline for next-pulse prediction. It's ready for the next pulse to implement and run.\n\n**Next step queued:** Execute the CFI-weighted compression experiment to validate whether downweighting CFI=0 invariants improves prediction accuracy. 1 mutation is pending implementation."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2598,"output":602,"cacheRead":12137,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15337,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774369611253}}
